A 20% global rise in measles cases in 2024 shows just how quickly diseases can return, even within a year. 
 
But this surge is preventable. Vaccines save lives. 
 
@UNICEF, in partnership with @gavi is working to prevent outbreaks by making vaccines accessible to every child. https://t.co/3e9RSMWfJu

